WEBVTT

00:05.273 --> 00:07.708
This is Air 3. We're over
here at the help call.

00:07.775 --> 00:10.244
Be advised,we have one male
downin the driveway.

00:10.311 --> 00:11.912
Advise rescue team
to respond,

00:11.979 --> 00:13.581
westbound to Bowcroft.

00:16.350 --> 00:18.619
Rescue team be advised,
possible sniper threat

00:18.686 --> 00:21.122
is in the hils south of
the victim's location.

00:36.003 --> 00:37.805
All right, move!

00:37.871 --> 00:39.340
Eyes on the hills.

01:03.197 --> 01:08.102
- Mount up! Mount up!
- Spread out! Go!

01:29.757 --> 01:31.692
**

01:52.079 --> 01:54.982
* I got a feeling
that I can't let go *

01:55.048 --> 01:57.551
